text: haey knongchamnaom mnoussaalok mean anakakhleah tinh peakyasaamdei lengsaech( avei del noam aoy phe l ch a l laoh) daembi thveu aoy anakadtei v nge v ng pi meakra robsa a l laoh daoy kmean chamnehdoeng haey ke yk vea( ayeat kuor an) toukchea kar chamak . puok teangnoh nung ttuol tearounakamm yeang ameasa bamphot
